<dfn>From</dfn>: Geoff Voelker &lt;<a href="mailto:voelker&#64;CS.UCSD.EDU?Subject=Re:%20SIGOPS-ANNOUNCE%20supplemental%20posting%20(OS%20Review%20Changes,%20CFP%20for%20PlanetLab%20special%20topics%20issue)">voelker@CS.UCSD.EDU</a>&gt;
